# Full Screen Quad Mesh for HeightFogComponent
# TL2 Engine - Z-up Left-handed coordinate system with DirectX 11
# Right-handed source (will be converted to left-handed by ObjManager)

# Object name
o FullScreenQuad

# Vertices (position) - Right-handed coordinates for ObjManager conversion
# Z-up 좌표계에서 화면은 XY 평면에 위치
# ObjManager에서 Y축이 뒤집어질 것을 고려하여 Y값에 -1을 곱함
v -1.0 -1.0  0.0    # Top-left (ObjManager will convert to: -1, 1, 0)
v  1.0 -1.0  0.0    # Top-right (ObjManager will convert to: 1, 1, 0)
v  1.0  1.0  0.0    # Bottom-right (ObjManager will convert to: 1, -1, 0)
v -1.0  1.0  0.0    # Bottom-left (ObjManager will convert to: -1, -1, 0)

# Texture coordinates - DirectX 11 convention (top-left origin)
# ObjManager에서 v = 1.0f - v 변환을 고려하여 미리 뒤집어서 정의
vt 0.0 1.0          # Top-left (after conversion: 0.0, 0.0)
vt 1.0 1.0          # Top-right (after conversion: 1.0, 0.0)
vt 1.0 0.0          # Bottom-right (after conversion: 1.0, 1.0)
vt 0.0 0.0          # Bottom-left (after conversion: 0.0, 1.0)

# Normals - Z축 방향 (화면을 향해)
# Z-up 좌표계에서 화면 효과는 일반적으로 +Z 방향
vn 0.0 0.0 1.0      # Forward normal (+Z direction)
vn 0.0 0.0 1.0      # Forward normal
vn 0.0 0.0 1.0      # Forward normal  
vn 0.0 0.0 1.0      # Forward normal

# Faces (using vertex/texture/normal indices)
# ObjManager에서 오른손→왼손 변환 시 버텍스 순서가 뒤집어질 것을 고려
# 최종적으로 반시계방향(CCW)이 되도록 시계방향(CW)으로 정의
f 1/1/1 3/3/3 2/2/2 # Triangle 1: 1 → 2 → 3
f 1/1/1 4/4/4 3/3/3  # Triangle 2: 1 → 3 → 4